<P>Here <HI>Antiphaus</HI> ro&s;e up from his &s;eat, and as <HI>Philyp&s;us</HI> perceiv'd that he had fini&s;h'd; "I was unwilling to interrupt you (&s;ays he) otherwi&s;e I &s;hou'd have ob&s;erv'd on a ver&s;e or two, which you repeated, as rough, and of a bad turn. What were tho&s;e Lines of <HI>the Roc<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">s,</HI> which you mention'd ju&s;t now?&mdash;Of the Rocks? (&s;ays <HI>Antiphaus)</HI> let me &s;ee&mdash;Oh, I remember them;
