<P><HI>Full</HI> &s;hines <HI>the Father</HI> in the <HI>Filial Frame, Od.</HI> 4, 199. He ceas'd: the <HI>Filial Virtue</HI> made reply. 22, 167. Mean time <HI>Arcte</HI> for the hour of re&s;t <HI>Ordains</HI> the fleecy couch&mdash;7, 428. The Peers reproach the &s;ure <HI>Divine</HI> of fate. 20, 432.</P>
