<L>Thou guardian power of <HI>Cill<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> the Divine,</L>
<L>Thou <HI>&s;ource of Light<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> whom <HI>T<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">dos</HI> adores.</L>
<L>And who&s;e <HI>bright</HI> pre&s;ence <HI>gilds</HI> thy <HI>Chry&s;a's</HI> &s;hore<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"></L>
<L>God of the Silver bow! thy Shafts employ,</L>
<L><NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot"><HI>Il.</HI> 1, 60&mdash;42.</NOTE> Avenge thy &s;ervant, and the <HI>Greeks</HI> de&s;troy.</L>
